Sophisticated Asset Allocation
Professional Money Management
Automatic Rebalancing

The Optimum Market Portfolios account packages a diverse series of mutual funds into a sophisticated asset allocation strategy that includes automatic portfolio rebalancing. It is designed to help investors meet their financial goals, while staying within a particular risk profile. Work with an AXA Advisors Financial Professional to create a personal risk profile.








Want more details on how this product may help you? Talk to a financial professional















Experience, balance, simplicity
Whether it’s building for retirement, establishing a legacy for loved ones or simply seeking wealth, we all invest with goals in mind.
Experience — The fund lineup in the Optimum Market Portfolios includes several money managers, who were selected based on the extensive experience they have in the asset classes they represent.
Balance — Keeping your investments on track is essential to a long-term strategy. The automatic rebalancing feature, standard in the Optimum Market Portfolios account, helps ensure that your portfolio stays on the course selected by you and your Financial Professional.
Simplicity — The Optimum Market Portfolios utilize in-depth research, providing you and your Financial Professional with a simple way to establish a professional asset allocation strategy suitable to your risk tolerance.
Automatic Rebalancing - you have just the tool you need to keep your portfolio in line with your target allocations. Based on your preference, investments within your portfolio are adjusted as needed on a quarterly, semiannual or annual basis.
For more information please explore our Optimum Markets Portfolio Client Brochure.










